reviewText: I was the producer of this tape. Thank you for the great comments.  It is a piece of wrestling history. I was the director of the first ladies cage match.

This video was so boring.  The wrestling was horrible.  The girls were not beautiful.  DO NOT BUY THIS!  I bought this based on the other people's reviews.  They must be talking about another video, because, I watched it  once, then threw it out.

I loved the tape and this one is a keeper.  My favorite match was the Cage Match where History was made in Women's Pro Wrestling. Just that match alone is worth the price of this tape.  Order yours today.
